30:34.939 --> 30:35.760
No, I don't think so.

30:35.780 --> 30:36.361
This afternoon.

30:36.882 --> 30:38.604
No, I don't think so.

30:38.985 --> 30:40.327
So they're going to go out there.

30:40.407 --> 30:43.932
And then they will be putting boxes out there and...

30:44.300 --> 30:45.622
store according to size.

